OL,3,CNational Museum Cardiff to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'essential' repairs
OL,6,FNational Museum Cardiff is set to
OL,7,Freopen to the public on Friday after
OL,8,Fcompleting "essential" repair work.
OL,10,FThe museum had suddenly closed on 2
OL,11,FFebruary due to a "mechanical" issue,
OL,12,Fwhich Amgueddfa Cymru said was caused
OL,13,Fby a "component failure in an isolated
OL,14,Farea of the building" and had required
OL,15,F"immediate attention."
