OL,3,CNational Museum Cardiff to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'essential' repairs
OL,6,FIn a statement, Amgueddfa Cymru said
OL,7,Fthe closure was necessary to
OL,8,Fprioritise the safety of visitors,
OL,9,Fvolunteers, and staff, as well as the
OL,10,Fpreservation of the museum's
OL,11,Fcollections.
OL,13,FThe museum's statement on Thursday
OL,14,Fread: "After completing essential
OL,15,Fmaintenance work, Amgueddfa Cymru is
OL,16,Fdelighted to announce it will be
OL,17,Freopening its doors to National Museum
OL,18,FCardiff on Friday 7 February.
