OL,3,CNational Museum Cardiff to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'essential' repairs
OL,6,F"Due to a mechanical issue caused by a
OL,7,Fcomponent failure in an isolated area
OL,8,Fof the building, on Sunday 02
OL,9,FFebruary, Amgueddfa Cymru had to make
OL,10,Fthe decision to temporarily close
OL,11,FNational Museum Cardiff to the public
OL,12,Ffor a short period.
OL,14,F"Our teams have since been working
OL,15,Fdiligently to undertake essential
OL,16,Frepairs as quickly and effectively as
OL,17,Fpossible to ensure the building meets
OL,18,Fall required safety standards
