OL,3,CNational Museum Cardiff to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'essential' repairs
OL,6,FChief Executive Jane Richardson said:
OL,7,F"Like so many institutions across
OL,8,FWales and the UK, managing and
OL,9,Fmaintaining aging buildings is an
OL,10,Fongoing challenge.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank all our staff
OL,13,Fand suppliers who have worked
OL,14,Ftirelessly to resolve the issue,
OL,15,Fminimising disruption for our
OL,16,Fvisitors."
OL,18,FThe closure had prompted concerns from
OL,19,Fpoliticians.
