OL,3,CNational Museum Cardiff to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'essential' repairs
OL,6,FHeledd Fychan, Member of the Senedd
OL,7,Ffor South Wales Central and Plaid
OL,8,FCymru's spokesperson for Finance and
OL,9,FCulture, had described the closure as
OL,10,F"a matter of real worry," highlighting
OL,11,Fthe impact on the public and the
OL,12,Fcultural sector.
OL,14,FWales' culture minister Jack Sargeant
OL,15,Fsaid that the contents of the museum
OL,16,Fwere protected during the closure.
OL,18,FHe told the Senedd on Wednesday: "Let
OL,19,Fme be clear, the museum is closed
OL,20,Fbecause of a mechanical issue, not a
OL,21,Fstructural issue.
